section.section:
A member is entitled to receive a normal service retirement allowance that equals:
an allowance based on the creditable service the member earned in the Employees' Pension System;
an allowance based on the creditable service the member earned in the Employees' Retirement System;
an allowance based on the creditable service the member earned in the Teachers' Pension System; plus
an allowance based on the creditable service the member earned in the Teachers' Retirement System.
